lopments in Ginzburg-Landau and microscopic\ndescriptions of this state.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Oct 2011 18:25:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Mar 2012 19:40:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-08-31"}
